<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>添加投票</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('head.ejs') %>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<div class="container">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg ">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/vote">决议列表</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/vote/create">创建议题</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <form class="d-flex" role="search">
                    <input class="form-control me-2" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" type="submit">Search</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="py-5 text-center">
        <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="/images/3.svg" alt="" width="72" height="57">
        <h3>创建议题 </h3>
        <p>欢迎来到我们的知识社区文章创建页面！我们的社区致力于为大家提供一个共享知识和经验的平台。
            我们相信每个人都有独特的想法和经验，而这些想法和经验可以为他人带来启发和帮助。因此，我们邀请您加入我们的社区，与全球的知识分享者们一起创造一个更美好的世界。创建过程非常简单，只需填写一些基本信息即可。快来加入我们吧！</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-5">
        <div class="modal-body p-5 col-md-5 col-lg-4 order-md-last">
            <h2 class="fw-bold mb-0">你将收获到</h2>

            <ul class="d-grid gap-4 my-5 list-unstyled">
                <li class="d-flex gap-4">
                    <!--                    <svg class="bi text-muted flex-shrink-0" width="48" height="48">-->
                    <!--                        <use xlink:href="#friends"></use>-->
                    <!--                    </svg>-->
                    <img src="/images/2.svg" alt="twbs" width="48" height="48" class="rounded-circle flex-shrink-0">
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0">兴趣相投的伙伴</h5>
                        A partner with similar interests
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="d-flex gap-4">
                    <img src="/images/4.svg" alt="twbs" width="48" height="48" class="rounded-circle flex-shrink-0">
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0">丰富的社区活动</h5>
                        Rich community activities
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="d-flex gap-4">
                    <img src="/images/5.svg" alt="twbs" width="48" height="48" class="rounded-circle flex-shrink-0">
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0">参与社区的决策发展</h5>
                        Participate in the decision-making development of the community
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="d-flex gap-4">
                    <img src="/images/6.svg" alt="twbs" width="48" height="48" class="rounded-circle flex-shrink-0">
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0">学习到多种多样的知识</h5>
                        Learn a variety of knowledge
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-8">
            <h3 class="mb-3">添加投票</h3>
            <hr>
            <form class="needs-validation" action="/vote/addDraft" method="post">
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label for="draftName">议题</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="draftName" name="draftName" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label for="topic">简介</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="topic" name="topic" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label for="draftDetail">详细介绍</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="draftDetail" name="draftDetail" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label for="communityId">所属论坛</label>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example" id="communityId" name="communityId" required>
                            <option selected>下拉选择一个论坛</option>
                            <% for (var i = 0; i < article.length; i++) { %>
                            <option value="<%= article[i].communityID %>"><%= article[i].comm_name%></option>
                           <% }%>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <label for="startTime">开始时间</label>
                        <input type="datetime-local" class="form-control" id="startTime" name="startTime" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <label for="endTime">结束时间</label>
                        <input type="datetime-local" class="form-control" id="endTime" name="endTime" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label for="number">最少投票人数</label>
                        <input type="number" class="form-control" id="number" name="number" required>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="my-4">
                    <button  type="submit" class="w-100 btn btn-primary btn-lg">提交</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('foot.ejs') %>
</div>
</body>
</html>
